-- EDF May Put 50% of French Grid RTE Into Nuclear Asset Decommissioning Fund
-- Tara Patel
-- 2010-07-21T06:30:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-21/edf-may-put-50-of-french-grid-rte-into-nuclear-asset-decommissioning-fund.html

          
          
             Electricite de France SA said in a
statement it is studying the possibility of putting 50 percent
of French grid RTE into a dedicated fund for decommissioning
nuclear assets.  
          
          


  


        